    <!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>NIM Game</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/loginStyle.css">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/loginScript.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="container">
        <!-- Left Box for Game Rules -->
        <div id="leftBox">
            <img src="/images/nim2.png" alt="Game NIM2">
            <p id="gameExplanations"><strong>NIM2:</strong> Divide packets of sticks</p>
            <ol>
                <p><strong>Game rules:</strong></p>

                <li>You can <strong> select </strong> <i> one, two or three </i> of sticks by just <strong>click</strong> on each stick you want to pick.</li>
                <li>You can't select sticks <i>more than 3 sticks</i>.</li>
                <li>You can <strong>unselect</strong> sticks by just <strong>click</strong> on the one you want to unselect.</li>
                <li>You can perform your move by <strong>click</strong> on the <i>Make move</i> button.</li>
                <li>The <i>game is over</i> when there still <i>only one stick</i> from all rows, and the looser is the one who pick up the last stick.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <!-- Center Box for Login -->
        <div id="loginContainer">
            <h1>Welcome to NIM Game</h1>
            <form id="loginForm">
                <label for="username">Enter your name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="username" required>
                <label for="gameType">Select game type:</label>
                <select id="gameType">
                    <option value="NIM1" selected>Pick up sticks from rows</option>
                    <option value="NIM2">Divide packets of sticks</option>
                </select>
                <br>
                <label for="level">Select the level:</label>
                <select id="level">
                    <option value="Easy" selected>Easy</option>
                    <option value="Medium">Medium</option>
                    <option value="Hard">Hard</option>
                </select>
                <br>
                <label>Select number of sticks:</label>
                <select id="sticks">
                    <option value="mode4">4</option>
                    <option value="mode9">9</option>
                    <option value="mode16" selected>16</option>
                </select>
                <button type="button" id="startButton" onclick="startGame()">Start Game</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Box for Game Rules -->
        <div id="rightBox">
            <img src="/images/nim1.png" alt="Game NIM1">
            <p id="gameExplanations"><strong>NIM1:</strong> Pick up sticks from rows</p>
            <ol>
                <p><strong>Game rules:</strong></p>

                <li>You can <strong> select </strong> any number of sticks <i>from the same row</i> by just <strong>click</strong> on each stick you want to pick.</li>
                <li>You can't select sticks <i>from two rows</i> at the same turn.</li>
                <li>You can <strong>unselect</strong> sticks by just <strong>click</strong> on the one you want to unselect, and if you unselect all sticks selected from a spicific row then you can select sticks from another row.</li>
                <li>You can perform your move by <strong>click</strong> on the <i>Make move</i> button.</li>
                <li>The <i>game is over</i> when there still <i>only one stick</i> from all rows, and the <i>looser</i> is the one who pick up the last stick.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

</body>
